1
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,560
Zhu Yihai

2
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:43,679
Chaoyang

3
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:45,600
Aren't you my son?

4
00:00:46,119 --> 00:00:48,679
You don't think 26 years in prison

5
00:00:48,679 --> 00:00:50,560
wipes the slate clean between us, do you?

6
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,479
Chaoyang

7
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,640
Help! Help! Somebody help!

8
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,359
Bro Hai

9
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,520
What's wrong with you?

10
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,880
I really did become Zhu Yihai.

11
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,879
Who is it?

12
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,760
Who's there?

13
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,599
Wha- what's with the getup?

14
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,560
Hold on, let me put my pants on.

15
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,680
What the hell is this?

16
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,159
Bro Hai, weren't you going to change?

17
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:45,200
What did I say?

18
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,439
That head injury definitely left some damage.

19
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:49,799
Da Hai

20
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,200
Who clawed up your face like that?

21
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,280
What's going on?

22
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,599
You hiding someone in there?

23
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,519
Let me see.

24
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,920
You really are hiding someone!

25
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,120
No way.

26
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:12,000
Oh my God!

27
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,360
He turned this place into a total mess.

28
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,639
Goodness, what a mess.

29
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,840
I'll pick out your outfits from now on.

30
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,560
Wear this one on Monday.

31
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:43,800
Tuesday...

32
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,199
this one.

33
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,039
Wednesday...

34
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,879
this'll do.

35
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,080
Zhu Yihai's a lucky man.

36
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,680
Looks great.

37
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,919
I can tell you're distracted.

38
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:07,879
What's up?

39
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,199
Thinking about the Aimin Street deal?

40
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,400
Tell me.

41
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,960
What's your plan once you get that land?

42
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:24,800
That spot will be mine sooner or later.

43
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,199
Damn right, Bro.

44
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,479
Boss Long.

45
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,479
What are you two doing in my office?

46
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,800
Bro.

47
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,719
Have a seat.

48
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,120
Xie Fan.

49
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,759
Do you have a problem with the Zhu Yihai thing?

50
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,560
Yeah.

51
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,560
But he did save my life.

52
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,000
I gotta show my appreciation somehow.

53
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,800
Fine.

54
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,960
Bro, you do your thing.

55
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,639
No problem with you being generous.

56
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,599
But I'd like to see...

57
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,759
that holdout on Aimin Street,

58
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,039
sly old Director Ge,

59
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,000
the steel mill demolition...

60
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,919
just what is Zhu Yihai capable of?

61
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,800
Xie Fan.

62
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,120
Ambition is a good thing.

63
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,399
But everything has consequences.

64
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,360
Think before you act.

65
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,720
Sure.

66
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,199
Manager Xie.

67
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,639
We really should think before we act.

68
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:41,639
Like hell we should.

69
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:51,279
Abracadabra!

70
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,480
This reading...

71
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:08,279
This reading's not bad.

72
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,800
Director Ge, sorry to bother you.

73
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:11,680
This here is...

74
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,720
the factory's remaining budget for this quarter.

75
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:15,680
Alright.

76
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,360
Got it.

77
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,319
So how should I handle this account?

78
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,800
I-I-I... I mean...

79
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,240
Here's the thing.

80
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,560
Put this money...

81
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,600
all into this account.

82
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,879
The rest...

83
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,600
I'll handle.

84
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,279
Got it.

85
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,399
So this money...

86
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:32,680
I'll keep this part.

87
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,560
Alright.

88
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,800
I'll head back then, Director Ge.

89
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:45,120
Damn, he skims even from this.

90
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,759
Having such a great boss

91
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:50,279
is truly our blessing.

92
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:15,519
Hey buddy, you look new around here.

93
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,759
You're not from our factory, are you?

94
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,480
Don't even get me started.

95
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,639
I just got transferred back from out of town.

96
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:23,399
How did your factory end up like this?

97
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,439
Boss Hu said the factory's been doing badly.

98
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:28,040
They're cutting part of it.

99
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,639
At first it all sounded pretty good.

100
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,839
Once we were laid off,

101
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:33,160
we'd get some compensation money.

102
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,759
We could even start a small business.

103
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:35,920
And then?

104
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,480
Then out of nowhere,

105
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,480
some son of a bitch shows up.

106
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,360
Sweet-talked us, swindled us.

107
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,120
Not only did we never see the money,

108
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,839
the factory ended up in debt too.

109
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,439
Sorry about that.

110
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:46,720
Did I hurt you?

111
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:50,680
Something like that happened?

112
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,639
Who's this son of a bitch?

113
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,319
Boss Hu said

114
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:56,000
he's from the Giant Wood Group.

115
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,720
The number two.

116
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,639
But we're just regular folks.

117
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:00,720
Never actually seen the guy.

118
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,360
Boss Hu said,

119
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,800
if he ever finds out who it is,

120
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,399
he'll skin him alive.

121
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,879
The number two of Giant Wood Group...

122
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,079
What, you know him?

123
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,279
Yeah, I know him.

124
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,079
Isn't that Zhu Yihai from our factory?

125
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,680
Hey, Sis.

126
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,199
Bro, if you keep doing that,

127
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,839
I can't give you a massage.

128
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,439
You know what, forget the massage.

129
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,399
Come with me.

130
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,480
I'll take care of you.

131
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:25,759
Come on.

132
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,240
Bro, bro, don't do that.

133
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,279
Bro.

134
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:29,639
Bro.

135
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,560
You just said

136
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,279
you know who the number two is, right?

137
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,199
I'm gonna build

138
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,959
a massive foot spa city

139
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,920
I've already got a name

140
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:40,959
What is it?

141
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,600
Monroe Foot Spa City

142
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,439
Why not Lili Foot Spa City?

143
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,839
You comparing yourself to Monroe?

144
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,480
Bro Hai

145
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,040
Why do you suddenly wanna do this?

146
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,959
What do you know?

147
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,480
This is the tertiary industry

148
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,160
You see?

149
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,839
Got it.

150
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,040
Alright.

151
00:07:58,319 --> 00:08:00,480
If Bro Hai does it, he'll be number one.

152
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,800
I'm with you.

153
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:03,759
Dali

154
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:04,759
You got any dreams?

155
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:05,759
Sure I do.

156
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,160
My dream

157
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:09,079
is to buy a huge basket of red bean buns

158
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,079
I wouldn't even eat them

159
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,279
Just look at them.

160
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,920
Then what's the point?

161
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,879
Just for the joy of it!

162
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,399
Look at how pathetic you are.

163
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,519
What about you?

164
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,240
I'm kinda embarrassed to say.

165
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,240
My dream

166
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,000
If I make it big,

167
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:25,399
I'd definitely get a dual-cassette four-speaker stereo.

168
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:28,199
Oh, so ambitious.

169
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,199
What about you, Lili? Your dream?

170
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,399
Me?

171
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,639
What dream could I possibly have?

172
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:37,000
Just don't do anything stupid, that's enough.

173
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,879
Oh boy.

174
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,000
You bunch of bastards

175
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
Which one's Zhu Yihai?

176
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,320
And who are you?

177
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,080
What do you want with Bro Hai?

178
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,679
My little sis told me

179
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:50,440
if there's a score to settle, find Zhu Yihai.

180
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:53,080
Which one of you sons of bitches is it?

181
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,000
Hey, buddy

182
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,440
You're Zhu Yihai, right?

183
00:08:58,639 --> 00:08:59,120
Me?

184
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,120
Pretty strong, huh?

185
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:02,759
Wait

186
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:03,759
Bro Hai

187
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,639
Don't fight.

188
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,600
Mind your own business!

189
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,279
Brother

190
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,720
My bro may have really wronged your sis

191
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,039
but I can't let you lay a hand on him.

192
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,039
Fine.

193
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,159
Good to know you're here.

194
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,759
Tonight at eight-thirty

195
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,120
bring your big guy,

196
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,240
Butterfly.

197
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:25,440
Let's settle this for real at the old station.

198
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,799
You know Night City's fighting rules, right?

199
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:29,320
No weapons in a Night City brawl.

200
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,440
Don't need you to tell me.

201
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,080
Good, as long as you know.

202
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,720
Hold on.

203
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,600
Small business here

204
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,639
Two bucks a head

205
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:39,519
counts the moment you step in.

206
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,320
Pay up if you've got money.

207
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,639
You think I owe you?

208
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,120
Take care now.

209
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:56,240
This old guy's even hooked up with someone's sister.

210
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,000
Bro Hai

211
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,080
Let's call for backup.

212
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,759
Just a few thugs from Dongxing Factory.

213
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:03,320
Did you see me take my hands out of my pockets?

214
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,559
We'll mess with them, no sweat.

215
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:23,679
What's wrong, Da Hai?

216
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:25,720
I figured I'd rub my temples

217
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,120
so I can remember what happened before

218
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,360
See if I can recall it

219
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:31,200
Bro, what do you need to remember?

220
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:33,440
That's the thing, I can't remember

221
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,679
That's why I'm trying to

222
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,120
How could I have hit on his sister?

223
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,600
Am I that kind of guy?

224
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,399
Yes
